  "title": "Assistant Service Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3000 - $4000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression\\</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Gul Circle (Company Transport Provided)</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8.15am to 5.15pm</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Responsible for outdoor and indoor repair work of all cleaning products</strong></li><li><strong>Mechanical preventive maintenance - verify mechanical faults, replacement of spare parts and repair</strong></li><li><strong>Work closely with service technicians for problem solving and coordinating jobs between field service and workshop repairs</strong></li><li>Required to work within the Company workshop where there is no outdoor repair</li><li>Any ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess at least a Professional Certificate/ Nitec in any Electrical & Electronic or Mechatronics Engineering or relevant qualification</li><li><strong>Experience in repair of forklifts, automobiles, heavy industrial equipment, and knowledge in engines, motors and electrical would be relevant and useful</strong></li><li><strong>Possess Class 3 driving license is an advantage</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
